#. <section class="sutta" id="an3.56"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an3.56:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 3"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 3"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an3.56:0.2"
msgid "6. Brāhmaṇavagga"
msgstr "6. Brahmins"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an3.56:0.3"
msgid "56. Palokasutta"
msgstr "56. Falling Apart"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi1.160"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an3.56:1.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho aññataro brāhmaṇamahāsālo yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami … pe … "
"ekamantaṃ nisinno kho so brāhmaṇamahāsālo bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr ""
"Then a well-to-do Brahmin went up to the Buddha, and seated to one side he "
"said to him:"

msgctxt "an3.56:1.2"
msgid ""
"“sutaṃ metaṃ, bho gotama, pubbakānaṃ brāhmaṇānaṃ vuddhānaṃ mahallakānaṃ "
"ācariyapācariyānaṃ bhāsamānānaṃ:"
msgstr ""
"“Master Gotama, I have heard that brahmins of the past who were elderly and "
"senior, the teachers of teachers, said:"

#. VAR: pubbe sudaṃ → pubbassudaṃ (bj, s1-3, km, pts1)
#. VAR: ahosi → hoti (bj, s1-3)
msgctxt "an3.56:1.3"
msgid ""
"‘pubbe sudaṃ ayaṃ loko avīci maññe phuṭo ahosi manussehi, kukkuṭasaṃpātikā "
"gāmanigamarājadhāniyo’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘In the old days this world was as crowded as hell, just full of people. The "
"villages, towns and capital cities were no more than a chicken’s flight "
"apart.’"

msgctxt "an3.56:1.4"
msgid ""
"Ko nu kho, bho gotama, hetu ko paccayo yenetarahi manussānaṃ khayo hoti, "
"tanuttaṃ paññāyati, gāmāpi agāmā honti, nigamāpi anigamā honti, nagarāpi "
"anagarā honti, janapadāpi ajanapadā hontī”ti?"
msgstr ""
"What is the cause, sir, what is the reason why these days human numbers have "
"dwindled, a decline in population is evident, and whole villages, towns, "
"cities, and countries have disappeared?”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an3.56:2.1"
msgid ""
"“Etarahi, brāhmaṇa, manussā adhammarāgarattā visamalobhābhibhūtā "
"micchādhammaparetā."
msgstr ""
"“These days, brahmin, humans just love illicit desire. They’re overcome by "
"immoral greed, and mired in wrong thoughts."

#. VAR: aññamaññaṃ → aññamaññassa (s1-3, pts1)
msgctxt "an3.56:2.2"
msgid ""
"Te adhammarāgarattā visamalobhābhibhūtā micchādhammaparetā tiṇhāni satthāni "
"gahetvā aññamaññaṃ jīvitā voropenti, tena bahū manussā kālaṃ karonti."
msgstr ""
"Taking up sharp knives, they murder each other. And so many people perish."

msgctxt "an3.56:2.3"
msgid ""
"Ayampi kho, brāhmaṇa, hetu ayaṃ paccayo yenetarahi manussānaṃ khayo hoti, "
"tanuttaṃ paññāyati, gāmāpi agāmā honti, nigamāpi anigamā honti, nagarāpi "
"anagarā honti, janapadāpi ajanapadā honti."
msgstr ""
"This is the cause, this is the reason why these days human numbers have "
"dwindled."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an3.56:3.1"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, brāhmaṇa, etarahi manussā adhammarāgarattā visamalobhābhibhūtā "
"micchādhammaparetā."
msgstr "Furthermore, because these days humans just love illicit desire …"

msgctxt "an3.56:3.2"
msgid ""
"Tesaṃ adhammarāgarattānaṃ visamalobhābhibhūtānaṃ micchādhammaparetānaṃ devo "
"na sammādhāraṃ anuppavecchati."
msgstr "the heavens don’t provide enough rain,"

msgctxt "an3.56:3.3"
msgid "Tena dubbhikkhaṃ hoti dussassaṃ setaṭṭhikaṃ salākāvuttaṃ."
msgstr ""
"so there’s famine, a bad harvest, with blighted crops that turn to straw."

msgctxt "an3.56:3.4"
msgid "Tena bahū manussā kālaṃ karonti."
msgstr "And so many people perish."

msgctxt "an3.56:3.5"
msgid ""
"Ayampi kho, brāhmaṇa, hetu ayaṃ paccayo yenetarahi manussānaṃ khayo hoti, "
"tanuttaṃ paññāyati, gāmāpi agāmā honti, nigamāpi anigamā honti, nagarāpi "
"anagarā honti, janapadāpi ajanapadā honti."
msgstr ""
"This is the cause, this is the reason why these days human numbers have "
"dwindled."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an3.56:4.1"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, brāhmaṇa, etarahi manussā adhammarāgarattā visamalobhābhibhūtā "
"micchādhammaparetā."
msgstr "Furthermore, because these days humans just love illicit desire …"

#. VAR: ossajjanti → ossajanti (bj)
msgctxt "an3.56:4.2"
msgid ""
"Tesaṃ adhammarāgarattānaṃ visamalobhābhibhūtānaṃ micchādhammaparetānaṃ "
"yakkhā vāḷe amanusse ossajjanti, tena bahū manussā kālaṃ karonti."
msgstr "native spirits let vicious monsters loose. And so many people perish."

msgctxt "an3.56:4.3"
msgid ""
"Ayampi kho, brāhmaṇa, hetu ayaṃ paccayo yenetarahi manussānaṃ khayo hoti, "
"tanuttaṃ paññāyati, gāmāpi agāmā honti, nigamāpi anigamā honti, nagarāpi "
"anagarā honti, janapadāpi ajanapadā hontī”ti."
msgstr ""
"This is the cause, this is the reason why these days human numbers have "
"dwindled.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "an3.56:5.1"
msgid "“Abhikkantaṃ, bho gotama … pe …"
msgstr "“Excellent, Master Gotama! Excellent!"

msgctxt "an3.56:5.2"
msgid ""
"upāsakaṃ maṃ bhavaṃ gotamo dhāretu ajjatagge pāṇupetaṃ saraṇaṃ gatan”ti."
msgstr ""
"From this day forth, may Master Gotama remember me as a lay follower who has "
"gone for refuge for life.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an3.56:5.3"
msgid "Chaṭṭhaṃ."
msgstr ""
